				<h1 class="name post-title entry-title" itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Thing"><span itemprop="name">US government sues Standard &#038; Poor&#8217;s after AAA downgrade</span></h1>

				
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="share-post">
